# 🌟 Vibrant To-Do List

A beautiful, high-performance To-Do application built with a **C++ logic mindset** and a **Modern Web Frontend**. This project features a glassmorphism design with a vibrant color palette, designed to make task management an eye-soothing experience.

## ✨ Features
- **Add Multiple Tasks:** Quickly add goals to your list.
- **Table Format:** View your tasks in a clean, organized table.
- **Status Tracking:** Mark tasks as `Pending` or `Completed` with a single click.
- **Toggle & Delete:** Easily manage your list with intuitive action buttons.
- **Persistent Storage:** Uses Browser LocalStorage so your tasks stay saved even after a refresh.
- **Vibrant UI:** A modern, responsive design using CSS Gradients and Flexbox.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3 (Custom Gradients), JavaScript (ES6)
- **Backend Logic:** C++ (Conceptual Architecture)
- **Version Control:** Git & GitHub

